{"tid":973423,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"如果阿媽唔係我阿媽","createTime":"2019-01-08T06:57:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-08T08:56:16.000Z","uid":221852,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3fd5271f4d21b6f0ed4d9f8022b1d7faf05b9af4","tid":973423,"uid":221852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T06:57:11.000Z","msg":"如果阿媽唔係我阿媽，仲要後生多20年，我會追我阿媽唔係講笑，我覺得自己阿媽真係完美嘅女性<br />\n煮飯煲湯唔洗講，冇其他野係比得上，款式眾多，又識整甜品糖水，仲要煮到好撚好食<br />\n會輪流同我洗衫煮飯做家務，唔會逼灑我做，有時知我返工攰做埋我個份（佢都要返工）<br />\n我比家用佢，佢會問返我夠唔夠錢洗，自己唔夠錢可以唔洗比佢，不過我都會比佢<br />\n性格溫和有禮，識得同人溝通，識得將心比己，有時覺得佢仲好人過頭添<br />\n最重要係相處舒服，完全冇港女屬性<br />\n而家香港真係搵唔到一個同我阿媽性格內涵同等級嘅女仔<br />\n阿媽我愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c55e21f43748cf7261cee818667291c949da6c63","tid":973423,"uid":107364,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T06:58:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5a7047b586f9d72897136522206096c93f8abbbf","tid":973423,"uid":221852,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c55e21f43748cf7261cee818667291c949da6c63","tid":973423,"uid":107364,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T06:58:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T07:09:16.000Z","msg":"Cls"},{"pid":"fb7cddef6bb04a14b53abb538c5ecd060f0c9109","tid":973423,"uid":53194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T08:18:55.000Z","msg":"戀母情結<br />\n<br />\nBTW 後生20年都大你一個圈"},{"pid":"145af40d639fbff2607393a7d2213d926cdf43ab","tid":973423,"uid":221852,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fb7cddef6bb04a14b53abb538c5ecd060f0c9109","tid":973423,"uid":53194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T08:18:55.000Z","msg":"戀母情結<br />\n<br />\nBTW 後生20年都大你一個圈"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T08:21:52.000Z","msg":"後生20年已經細過我 sorry"},{"pid":"985fa05ab0125a36525c68ae85ea88666d950be8","tid":973423,"uid":128741,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"145af40d639fbff2607393a7d2213d926cdf